description:
You'll fairly float into the party in this creation, made of sheer georgette. The tunic-length jacket's hemline dips to points in front and back. Sleeveless, fully-lined pullover dress has two fluttering tiers. Hits at knee.

  • Neckline: Jewel
  • Sleeve Length: Long
  • Length: Dress length from natural waist: Misses and Women's 25''; Petites 24''
  • Content: 100% Polyester
  • Care: Machine wash.
  • Origin: Imported


Why We Love It

This is it! More than just a jacket dress, this look is our customers' #1 outfit for parties, weddings, New Year's Eve celebrations, graduations, everything! Designed in a premium georgette fabric, it's cut at various angles to create incredible flow. Truly, your every move will be captured with grace and finesses. And the flattery--wow! Every woman of every size looks her very best in this special occasion dress. Which is why we offer it in so many brilliant colors. But don't just take our word for its, here's what one of our happy customers had to say: "I ordered this dress for my 86-year-old mom to wear as grandmother of the bride at a spring wedding. We live several hours apart so had to shop long-distance and hope for the best. We opted for the express shipping, and Mom called three days later, reporting that the packaging was nice, the dress fit, the style was appropriate and becoming, the length was perfect, and color and fabric were "lovely". The pink was exactly the shade she had hoped for. Mom was very, very pleased with this choice, and I am just delighted that she has a becoming outfit for the wedding--and we found it on the first try!" -- StylistForMom, Georgetown, TX
